[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "まったく……急に来たと思ったら、\nゼロと話がしたいなんて驚いたよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_01036",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "てへっ……許してくれてホント助かるわ、クレオ。\nすっごくありがと！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01037",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "私は寛大なことに定評があるからね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_01038",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヘルトの様子はどう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01039",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "まだ相変わらず、かな。声をかけても、一切反応を\n示さなくて、むしろ悪化している気すらするよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_01040",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そっか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01041",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ゼロ。今日はあんたと話をしに来たわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01042",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "ん？　我か？\nなんじゃ、何用じゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01043",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヘルトのことよ。あんたになら、ヘルトがどうして\n今の状態になってるか分かるかなって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01044",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "それをちょっと深いところで、考えたくってさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01045",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "そんなの、決まっとろう！　深くいく必要もない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01046",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "え、分かるの！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01047",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "兄者は、うぬらに負けたのが悔しいんじゃ！\nそうに決まっとる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01048",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……えぇ？　ほ、本当に、\nそんな子どもっぽい理由？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01049",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "そうじゃ、絶対そうじゃ。\n兄者は今まで負けなし。ゆえに一等悔しいのじゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01050",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うーん、初めての敗北に悔しくなるのは分かるけど、\nそれであそこまで落ち込むかしら……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01051",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あんたたちはパルメ族の命令で動いていたのよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01052",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "我も兄者も、パルメ族の命令には従わぬ！\n我らは我らの好きなように生きるんじゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01053",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "まぁ、我と兄者を強く創ったことには\n感謝してやらんでもないがな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01054",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "うぬは可哀そうじゃのお。調合機能なぞという、\n余計なものに力を割り振られてしまって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01055",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "余計なものじゃないわよ！\n……って、そっか。あんたらは錬金術を使えないのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01056",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "我らはパルメ族を守るため、脅威に対抗するために\nただ強くあれと創られたからの。最強であれ、と",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01057",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "最強……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01058",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "そうだよね。世界の管理者を名乗っていても、\n強くなければ管理はできないし、民も従わない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_01059",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "もしかしたら、ヘルトにも重圧があったのかも。\n最初の九偉人として誰よりも強くなければ、みたいなね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_01060",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "重圧？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01061",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "うん。自分に向けられる期待ってさ、嬉しい反面\n重いんだ。立場があると、余計に",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_01062",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "兄者は強いのだから、そんな重圧を感じるはずない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01063",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "兄には、妹には分からない重責があるのかもよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_01064",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ヘルトにも、そう思うことがあったのかしら……\n　最強でなければという、重圧……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01065",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（確かにゼロの言う通り、しっくりはこない。\n　でもクレオの言いたいことも分かる）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01066",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……ありがとう、二人とも。\nヘルトのこと、少し分かった気がする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01067",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "他の兄弟たちからも、話を聞いてみる。\nヘルトのこと、もっと知って理解したいし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01068",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "なぜ、兄者のことを理解したいのじゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01069",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なぜって……あんなことあったけど、兄弟だし、\n今のヘルトが心配だから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01070",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……記憶をなくした時、私は生きる目的も理由も\n分からなくなって、空っぽだった。けど――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01071",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そんな私を、ハイディたち家族が支えてくれた。\nおかげで、今の元気いっぱいな私がいるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01072",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "だから私も、家族として今のヘルトに\n何かできないかなって思うのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01073",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "……そうか。\n兄者の話であれば、また聞きに来るがよい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01074",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ありがとう、ゼロ。もっとヘルトのことを知って、\nまた会いに来るわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01075",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "クレオ！　それまで、この二人のことよろしく！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01076",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "分かった！\n二人の身柄は国で責任をもって預かってるね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_01077",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "さ、次は誰に話を聞きに行こうかしら",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01078",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]